//funcion de mabaya
function isCategory() {
    return /\/category\//.test(document.URL) ? true : false;
}

function widgetType(bool) {
    if (bool) {
        return "widgets=gallery_page_g1";
    } else {
        return "widgets=search_page_w1";
    }

}

function getSection(bool) {
    if (bool) {

        var match = document.URL.match(/cat\d+\/(.*)\?|cat\d+\/(.*)$/);
        var section = match[2] ? match[2] : match[1];
        return section.toLowerCase();
    } else {
         var queryString = window.location.search;
        var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(queryString);
        var redirectValue=urlParams.get('sred');
        if(redirectValue){
            return redirectValue.toLowerCase();
        }
        if(_satellite.getVar('search_SearchTerm')){
          return _satellite.getVar('search_SearchTerm').replace('BCR_', '').toLowerCase();
        }
        
        return document.URL.split('/')[5];
    }

}
function deleteExtraClones() {
    document.querySelectorAll('.mabayaClone').forEach(function(el) {
        el.remove();
    });
}

function showOrhideDuplicates(arr) {
    if (arr) {
        arr.forEach(function(el) {
            var duplicatePod = document.querySelector('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"], .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"], .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"]');
            if (duplicatePod && duplicatePod.closest('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)')) {
                duplicatePod.closest('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)').classList.add('hide');
            }
        });
    } else {
        if (document.querySelector('.hide.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)')) {
            document.querySelector('.hide.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)').classList.remove('hide');

        }
    }

}

function isFirstPage() {
    return true;
}
function isGoodOrderBy() {
    if (/marca|precio/i.test(_satellite.getVar('PLPOrderby'))) {
        return false
    }
    return true;
}
function getTag() {

    var params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.href);
    var arr = [];
    var _iteratorNormalCompletion = true;
    var _didIteratorError = false;
    var _iteratorError = undefined;

    try {
        for (var _iterator = params.entries()[Symbol.iterator](), _step; !(_iteratorNormalCompletion = (_step = _iterator.next()).done); _iteratorNormalCompletion = true) {
            pair = _step.value;
            var a = pair[0] + ": " + decodeURIComponent(pair[1]);
            var b = a.replace("::", " | ");
            arr.push(b);
        }
    } catch (err) {
        _didIteratorError = true;
        _iteratorError = err;
    } finally {
        try {
            if (!_iteratorNormalCompletion && _iterator.return != null) {
                _iterator.return();
            }
        } finally {
            if (_didIteratorError) {
                throw _iteratorError;
            }
        }
    }

    var newArr = arr.filter(function(el, index) {
        var temp;
        if (index === 0 && /\?/.test(el)) {
            temp = el.match(/\?(.*)/)[1];
        }
        if (index > 0) {

            temp = el;
        }
        if (/f\./.test(temp) && !/price|brand/.test(temp)) {

            return temp;
        }
    });
    var arr2 = newArr.map(function(a) {
        //return a.match(/\:(.*)/)[1].replace(/^\s/gi, '').replace(/\s\|\s|\:\:/gi, '|').toLowerCase();
        return a.match(/\:(.*)/)[1].replace(/\s/gi, '').replace(/\:\:/gi, '|').toLowerCase();
    }).join('|');

    if (arr2 === "") {
        return '';
    } else {
        return 'tag:' + arr2 + ',';
    }
}

function mabayaAdRequest(callback, callback2) {
    var IsCategory = isCategory();
    var storeHash = "storeHash=570436b118e98697c04269e8ee598adfd5e1f5a7f2fe3dab21da19f1c04fbd2b";
    var pageTypeParam = IsCategory ? "pageType=category" : "pageType=search";
    var mabayaRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
    var signal = "signal=" + encodeURIComponent(getSection(IsCategory)).toLowerCase();
    var ufObject = {
        brands: '',
        minPrice: '',
        maxPrice: '',
        cat: IsCategory ? "cid:" + document.URL.match(/(cat\d+)\//)[1] + "," : ""
    };

    var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
    if (urlParams.get('f.product.brandName') !== null) {

        urlParams.get('f.product.brandName').split('::').forEach(function(el) {
            ufObject.brands = ufObject.brands + 'brand:' + el.toLowerCase() + ',';
        });
    }
    var customPrice = urlParams.get('r.derived.price.search');
    if (urlParams.get('r.derived.price.search') !== null) {
        ufObject.minPrice = 'minPrice:' + customPrice.split('::')[1] + ',';
        ufObject.maxPrice = 'maxPrice:' + customPrice.split('::')[0] + ',';
    }

    var rangePrice = urlParams.get('f.range.derived.price.search');
    if (rangePrice !== null) {
        ufObject.minPrice = 'minPrice:' + rangePrice.split(' - ')[0].replace(/\$|\./g, '') + ',';
        ufObject.maxPrice = 'maxPrice:' + rangePrice.split(' - ')[1].replace(/\$|\./g, '') + ',';

    }
    var ufParam = "uf=" + encodeURIComponent(ufObject.cat + ufObject.brands + ufObject.minPrice + ufObject.maxPrice + getTag());
var ufPlatform= screen.width>1024?"desktop":"mobile";
    var paramString = widgetType(IsCategory) + "&" + storeHash + "&" + pageTypeParam + "&platform="+ufPlatform + "&" + signal + "&" + ufParam + "&url=" + encodeURIComponent(document.URL).toLowerCase();
    var mabayaURL = "https://us.widget.mb-srv.com/v2/server2server/ad.json?" + paramString;
    deleteExtraClones();
    showOrhideDuplicates();
    mabayaRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {
        var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
        if (isFirstPage() && isGoodOrderBy() && response.code && response.code === "OK" && response.payload.ads.length > 0) {
            if (callback) {

                //showOrhideDuplicates(response.payload.ads);
                callback(response.payload.ads, callback2);
            } else {
                console.log(response);
            }

        } else {
            console.log("no mabaya pods");
        }
        if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
            console.log("Error retrieving mabaya products")

        }
    });

    mabayaRequest.open("GET", mabayaURL, true);
    mabayaRequest.send();
}

function fixArr(arr) {
    if (typeof (arr) === "object" && arr[0] && arr[0].skuId) {
        return arr;
    }

    if (typeof (arr) === undefined) {
        return null;
    }
    var temporalArr = [];
    if (Array.isArray(arr)) {
        temporalArr = arr;
    }
    if (typeof (arr) === "string") {
        temporalArr = arr.split(",");
    }

    var fixedArray = []
    temporalArr.forEach(function(el) {
        fixedArray.push({
            "skuId": el
        });
    });
    return fixedArray;

}
function fetchProductUpdatedInfo(skuArr, callback) {
    //XMLHttpRequest
    window.mabayaIDs = {}
    skuArr.forEach(function(el) {
        window.mabayaIDs[el.sku] = el.mabaya_ad_info;
    });
    if (skuArr) {
        var newArr = skuArr.map(function(e) {
            return e.sku
        });

        var fetchItemDetailRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
        var fetchItemDetailURL = "/s/browse/v1/fetchItemDetails/co?" + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify({
            "products": fixArr(newArr)
        }));

        fetchItemDetailRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {

            var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
            if (response.success && response.success === true) {
                if (callback) {
                    showOrhideDuplicates(response.products);

                    callback(response.products);
                } else {
                    console.log(response.products, skuArr);
                }
            }

            if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
                callback(null);

            }
        });

        fetchItemDetailRequest.open("GET", fetchItemDetailURL, true);
        fetchItemDetailRequest.send();
    }
}
function patrocinadoLabel() {
    var pLabel = document.createElement('div');
    pLabel.classList.add('pod-sponsored-prod')
    pLabel.innerText = "Patrocinado";
    return pLabel;
}

function clonePodsWithInfo(res, objArr) {
    res.forEach(function(e, index) {
        
        if (document.querySelectorAll('.mabayaClone').length >= 6 || e.product.published != true) {
            return;
        }

        var allPods = document.querySelectorAll('.search-results-list:not(.mabaya), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabaya), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabaya)');

        if (index >= 2) {
            var repeatFlag = false;
            for (var i = 0; i > 12; i++) {
                if (allPods[i] !== undefined && allPods[i].querySelector('[data-key]').dataset.key == e.product.id) {
                    repeatFlag = true;

                }
            }
            if (repeatFlag) {
                return
            }

        }

        var newPod = allPods[0].cloneNode(true);
        newPod.classList.add("mabayaClone");
        newPod.classList.remove("hide");
        var mbid = window.mabayaIDs && window.mabayaIDs[e.product.id] ? window.mabayaIDs[e.product.id] : "";
        newPod.dataset.mbid = mbid;
        var mbidParam = mbid ? "&mbid=" + mbid : "";
        newPod.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(function(l) {
            l.href = e.product.url + "?MID=SP" + mbidParam;
        })

        newPod.querySelector('img').src = "https://falabella.scene7.com/is/image/FalabellaCO/" + e.product.id + "?wid=340&hei=340&qlt=70";
        newPod.querySelector('img').srcset = "https://falabella.scene7.com/is/image/FalabellaCO/" + e.product.id + "?wid=340&hei=340&qlt=70";
        if (e.product.badges && newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper')) {
            newPod.querySelectorAll('[class*=pod-badges-item]').forEach(function(badge) {
                badge.remove();
            });
            e.product.badges.forEach(function(badge) {
                var newBadge = document.querySelector('[class*=pod-badges-item]').cloneNode(true);

                newBadge.style.backgroundColor = badge.styles.backgroundColor;
                newBadge.style.textColor = badge.styles.textColor;
                newBadge.innerHTML = badge.label;
                newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper .pod-badges').appendChild(newBadge);
            });
        } else if (!e.product.badges && newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper .pod-badges').remove();
        }

        var bottomSpecifications = newPod.querySelector('.section__pod-bottom-description');

        if (bottomSpecifications) {
            bottomSpecifications.innerHTML = "";
            e.product.topSpecifications.forEach(function(el3) {

                var newSpecification = document.querySelector('.section__pod-bottom-description>li').cloneNode(false);
                newSpecification.innerText = el3;

                bottomSpecifications.appendChild(newSpecification);
            })

        }

        newPod.querySelectorAll('.ratings--container i').forEach(function(star, index) {

            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_full_filled');
            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_no_filled');
            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_half_filled');
            if (e.product.rating < 0 + 1) {
                star.classList.add("csicon-star_no_filled")
            } else {
                star.classList.add("csicon-star_full_filled");
            }
        });
        if (newPod.querySelector('.reviewCount')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.reviewCount').remove();
        }

        if (newPod.querySelector('.fa--color-swatch')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.fa--color-swatch').remove();
        }

        if (newPod.querySelector('.tab')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.tab').remove();
        }
        //csicon-star_full_filled
        //csicon-star_no_filled
        if (newPod.querySelector('.pod-subTitle')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-subTitle').innerText = e.product.displayName;
        }
        if (e.product.brand && newPod.querySelector('.pod-title')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-title').innerText = e.product.brand;
        }else{
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-title').remove();
        }

        if(newPod.querySelector('.pod-sellerText')){
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-sellerText').innerText="Por Falabella";
        }

            makeNewPrices(newPod, e.product.prices);
      
      
        if (newPod.querySelector('.pod-meta') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-meta').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), newPod.querySelector('[class*="action-button-place-holder"]'));
        } else if (newPod.querySelector('.section-body--right') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {

            newPod.querySelector('.section-body--right').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), null);

        } else if (newPod.querySelector('.section-head') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.section-head').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), null);
        }

        var childRefNode;
        if (index < 2) {
            childRefNode = allPods[0];
        } else if (index < 4) {
            childRefNode = allPods[13];
        } else {
            childRefNode = null;
        }

        document.querySelector('.search-results--products').insertBefore(newPod, childRefNode);

    });
    if (window.mabayaWidget) {
        window.mabayaWidget.track();
    }
}
//extension resource overrides

function makeNewPrices(node, price) {

    node.querySelectorAll('.fa--prices .price-0,.fa--prices .price-1,.fa--prices .price-2').forEach(function(el) {
        el.remove();
    });
    if (price[0]) {
        var newPrice = document.querySelector('.fa--prices .price-0').cloneNode(true);
        newPrice.querySelector('span').innerText = price[0].symbol + " " + price[0].originalPrice + " " + price[0].label;

        node.querySelector('.fa--prices').appendChild(newPrice);

    }
    if (price[1]) {
        var newPriceTwo = document.querySelector('.fa--prices .price-1').cloneNode(true)
        newPriceTwo.querySelector('span').innerText = price[1].symbol + " " + price[1].originalPrice + " " + price[1].label;
        node.querySelector('.fa--prices').appendChild(newPriceTwo);

    }

}

mabayaAdRequest(fetchProductUpdatedInfo, clonePodsWithInfo);

function insertMabayaScript(d) {
    var mabaya = d.createElement("script");
    mabaya.type = "text/javascript";
    mabaya.async = true;
    mabaya.src = "//us.widget.mb-srv.com/load.js?tag=falabellaCO-general";
    mabaya.id = "mabayaLoader";
    var ref = d.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
    ref.parentNode.insertBefore(mabaya, ref);
}

<script>_satellite["_runScript7"](function(event, target, Promise) {
var pageName=_satellite.getVar('page_pageType')?_satellite.getVar('page_pageType'):_satellite.getVar('page_pageName');
switch (pageName) {
	case 'product detail page':
		syteDataLayer = window.syteDataLayer || [];
		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'fe_page_view',
			tag: 'ecommerce',
			sku: _satellite.getVar('ecom_sku')
		});
		break;
	case 'basket':

    if(digitalData.ecom.productList.length!==0){
      syteDataLayer = window.syteDataLayer || [];
		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'checkout_start',
			tag: 'ecommerce',
			value: getTotal(),
			currency: 'COP',
			products: getProd()
		});
  
    }
		
		break;
	default:
		syteDataLayer = window.syteDataLayer || [];
		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'fe_page_view',
			tag: 'ecommerce'
		});

		break;
}


function getProd() {

	var prodsArr = []
	digitalData.ecom.productList.forEach(function (el) {
		var tempObj = {
			'sku': el.sku,
			'price': el.price,
			'quantity': el.quantity
		};
		prodsArr.push(tempObj);
	});
	return prodsArr;
}

function getTotal() {
	var total = 0;
	digitalData.ecom.productList.forEach(function (el) {
		total = el.price + total;
	})
	return total;
}
});</script>

function isDeviceMobile() {
  var isMobile = false;
  if (/Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|BB|PlayBook|IEMobile|Windows Phone|Kindle|Silk|Opera Mini/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
      isMobile = true;
  }
  return isMobile;
}

function hideAmanda() {
	var chatAmanda = document.querySelector('.chat-widget');
	if (chatAmanda) {  
		chatAmanda.style.display = "none";
	}
}

if (isDeviceMobile()) {
  hideAmanda();
  setInterval(hideAmanda, 1000);
}

  api: {
    rgx: function rgx(str) {
      var regex = new RegExp(str);
      return regex;
    }
  },
  elements: {
    checkForElement: function checkForElement(element, callback) {
      var el = element;
      var interval = setInterval(function (e) {
        var theElement = document.getElementById(el) || document.querySelectorAll(el);
        if (theElement.length === 0 || theElement === null) return;
        callback();
        clearInterval(interval);
      }, 400);
    },
    transformToArray: function transformToArray(el) {
      el = [].slice.apply(el);
      return el;
    },
    onBody: function onBody(bool, str) {
      if (bool) {
        document.body.classList.add(str);
      } else {
        document.body.classList.remove(str);
      }
    },
    createContainer: function createContainer(htmltag, strclass) {
      var innerInfo = arguments.length > 2 && arguments[2] !== undefined ? arguments[2] : '';
      var a = document.createElement(htmltag);
      a.className = strclass;
      a.innerHTML = innerInfo;
      return a;
    }
  },
  url: {
    checkUrlParams: function checkUrlParams(url, param) {
      var urlAccepted;
      var params = param;

      if (url.includes(params)) {
        urlAccepted = true;
      }

      return urlAccepted;
    }
  },
  network: {
    intercepter: function intercepter(callback) {
      var oldXHROpen = window.XMLHttpRequest.prototype.open;

      window.XMLHttpRequest.prototype.open = function (method, url, async, user, password) {
        // do something with the method, url and etc.
        this.addEventListener('load', function (e) {
          //console.log('load: ' + this.responseURL);
          var thisResponse = this.response === '' || this.reponse === undefined ? this.response : JSON.parse(this.response);
          callback(this.readyState, this.responseURL, thisResponse);
        });
        return oldXHROpen.apply(this, arguments);
      };
    },
    validateIntercep: function validateIntercep(state, element, url) {
      var pageValid = false;

      try {
        if (state !== 4) return;
        var checkHttpRequest = tools.api.rgx('confirm-your-order').test(url);
        if (!checkHttpRequest) return;
        var deliverySummary = document.getElementById(element);
        if (!deliverySummary.length) return;
        pageValid = true;
      } catch (e) {
        console.log('problem in validatePage(fn)/delivery -', e);
      }

      return pageValid;
    }
  },

      var itsOkay;
      if (windoWidth < 521) itsOkay = true;
      return itsOkay;
    }
  },

    removeSpecial: function removeSpecial(str) {

    }

var ui = {
    findNodesToInsert: function() {
        var secondLevelItems = document.querySelectorAll('.secondLevelMenu');
        if(!secondLevelItems.length) return;
        var arrSecondlevelItems = [].slice.apply(secondLevelItems);
        // find each case
        arrSecondlevelItems.map(function(el){
            var arrSecontParent = el;
            //if(el.querySelector('.sale_ticket')) return;
            var thirdMenu = el.querySelectorAll('a[class*="thirdLevelMenu"]');
            var arrThirdMenu = [].slice.apply(thirdMenu);
            var firstArrX = arrThirdMenu[0];
            var lastArrX = arrThirdMenu[arrThirdMenu.length -2]
            if(arrThirdMenu.length){
                arrThirdMenu.map(function(el){
                    var text = el.textContent.normalize('NFD').replace(/[^\w\s]/gi, '').toLowerCase();
                    if (/nuevo/.test(text) && firstArrX.textContent === el.textContent) {
                        if(text.length >= 22) return;
                        ui.addSaleSpan(el, arrSecontParent,'sale_ticket new','NUEVO', true);
                        // thirdMenu.setAttribute('href', 'https://www.falabella.com/falabella-cl/page/Navidad-Decoracion?staticPageId=39400001');
                    }
                    if (/sale/.test(text) && lastArrX.textContent === el.textContent) {
                        if(text.length >= 22) return;
                        ui.addSaleSpan(el, arrSecontParent,'sale_ticket sale','SALE', false);
                        // thirdMenu.setAttribute('href', 'https://www.falabella.com/falabella-cl/page/Navidad-Decoracion?staticPageId=39400001');
                    } 
                });
            }
        });
    },
    addSaleSpan: function(el,parent, thisClass, thisTxt, bool){
        //var newSpan = document.createElement('span');
        //newSpan.className = 'sale_ticket new';
        //newSpan.innerText = 'NUEVO';
        //el.innerText = el.innerText.replace(/SALE/g,'').trim();
        if(bool){
            if(parent.parentElement.querySelector('.sale_ticket.new'))return;
            el.innerText = el.innerText.replace('NUEVO','').trim();
            if(el.querySelector('.sale_ticket.new'))return;
            el.appendChild(template.label(thisClass, thisTxt));
        }
        if(!bool){
            if(parent.parentElement.querySelector('.sale_ticket.sale'))return;
            var a = el.innerText.toLowerCase().replace('sale','').trim();
            el.innerText = a.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + a.slice(1);
            // el.innerText = el.innerText.replace('SALE','').trim();
            if(el.querySelector('.sale_ticket.sale'))return;
            el.appendChild(template.label(thisClass, thisTxt));
        }
    }

var api = {
    getAccengageCurrentDate: function(x){
        var hours = x.toString().match(/\d\d:\d\d:\d\d/);
        var day = x.getDate();
        var month = x.getMonth() + 1;
        var year = x.getFullYear();
        var string = year + '-' + month + '-' + day + ' ' + hours;
        return string;    
    }
}
function isSLP(){
    if(digitalData.page.catalyst){
      return true;   
    }
  return false;
}
function accPdpWindowLoads(){
    if (/product/.test(window.location.href)) {
        if(isSLP()){
            if (!window.ACC) return;
            var prices = _satellite.getVar('recs_prices');
            var sku = _satellite.getVar('recs_productSku');
            var imageURL = document.querySelector('[id*="testId-pod-image"]') && document.querySelector('[id*="testId-pod-image"]').getAttribute('src');
            var productName;
            if (document.querySelector('.product-name')) {
                productName = document.querySelector('.product-name').textContent;
            } else {
                productName = undefined;
            }
            var PDPoptions = {
                'view_last_product_sku': sku,
                'view_last_product_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                'view_last_product_url': window.location.href.split('?')[0].split('/N-')[0],
                'view_last_product_price': prices.INTERNET || prices.NORMAL,
                'view_last_product_name': productName,
                'view_last_product_urlimage': imageURL,
                'view_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'), 
                'view_last_product_category_name': _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat1')
            };
            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", PDPoptions]);
        }else{
            if (!window.ACC) return;
            var prices = _satellite.getVar('recs_prices');
            var sku = _satellite.getVar('recs_productSku');
            var imageURL = document.querySelector('.js-pp-gallery-link img') && document.querySelector('.js-pp-gallery-link img').getAttribute('src');
            var productName;
            if (document.querySelector('.fb-product-cta__title')) {
                productName = document.querySelector('.fb-product-cta__title').textContent;
            } else {
                productName = undefined;
            }
            var PDPoptions = {
                'view_last_product_sku': sku,
                'view_last_product_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                'view_last_product_url': window.location.href.split('?')[0].split('/N-')[0],
                'view_last_product_price': prices.INTERNET || prices.NORMAL,
                'view_last_product_name': productName,
                'view_last_product_urlimage': imageURL,
                'view_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'),
                'view_last_product_category_name':digitalData.ecom && digitalData.ecom.cat1?digitalData.ecom.cat1:'' 
            };

            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", PDPoptions]);
        }
    }
}

    accPdpWindowLoads();
})();

(function (open) {
    XMLHttpRequest.prototype.open = function (method, callurl, async, user, pass) {
        this.addEventListener("readystatechange", function () {
            if(/(addItemToBasket)/.test(this.responseURL)){
                if (this.readyState === 4) {
                    if(isSLP()){
                        var theResponse = JSON.parse(this.response);
                        if (theResponse.success === true) {
                            if (!window.ACC) return;
                            var cat1 = _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat1');
                            var cat2 = _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2') === null || _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2') === undefined ? '' : " | ".concat(_satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2'));
                            var categories = cat1 + cat2;
                            //BASKET
                            var addToBasketOptions = {
                                'basket_last_product_name': theResponse.state.products[0].name,
                                'basket_last_product_urlimage': theResponse.state.products[0].image.file.replace('http','https'),
                                'basket_last_product_sku': theResponse.state.products[0].skuId,
                                'basket_last_product_url': 'https://www.falabella.com' + theResponse.state.products[0].url,
                                'basket_last_add_cart_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                                'basket_last_product_price': theResponse.state.products[0].price.slice(-1)[0].purchasedPrice,
                                'basket_last_product_category': categories,
                                // 'basket_last_product_category_id': digitalData.ecom.backend === null || digitalData.ecom.backend === undefined ? '' : digitalData.ecom.backend,
                                'basket_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'),
                                'basket_last_product_category_name':cat1

                            };
                            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", addToBasketOptions]);
                        }
                    }else{
                        var theResponse = JSON.parse(this.response);
                        if (theResponse.success === true) {
                            if (!window.ACC) return;
                            var getDigitalDataEcom = digitalData.ecom;
                            var cat1 = getDigitalDataEcom.cat1;
                            var cat2 = getDigitalDataEcom.cat2 === null || getDigitalDataEcom.cat2 === undefined ? '' : " | ".concat(getDigitalDataEcom.cat2);
                            var categories = cat1 + cat2;
                            //BASKET
                            var addToBasketOptions = {
                                'basket_last_product_name': theResponse.state.products[0].name,
                                'basket_last_product_urlimage': theResponse.state.products[0].image.file.replace('http','https'),
                                'basket_last_product_sku': theResponse.state.products[0].skuId,
                                'basket_last_product_url': 'https://www.falabella.com' + theResponse.state.products[0].url,

                                'basket_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'),
                                'basket_last_product_category_name':cat1

                            };
                            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", addToBasketOptions]);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }, false);
        open.call(this, method, callurl, async, user, pass);
    };

function fixArr(arr) {
    if (typeof (arr) === "object" && arr[0] && arr[0].skuId) {
        return arr;
    }

    if (typeof (arr) === undefined) {
        return null;
    }
    var temporalArr = [];
    if (Array.isArray(arr)) {
        temporalArr = arr;
    }
    if (typeof (arr) === "string") {
        temporalArr = arr.split(",");
    }

    var fixedArray = []
    temporalArr.forEach(function(el) {
        fixedArray.push({
            "skuId": el
        });
    });
    return fixedArray;

}

function fetchProductUpdatedInfo(skuString, callback) {

    //XMLHttpRequest
    var skuObj = fixArr(skuString);
    if (skuObj) {
        var fetchItemDetailRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
        var fetchItemDetailURL = "/s/browse/v1/fetchItemDetails/co?" + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify({
            "products": skuObj
        }));

        fetchItemDetailRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {

                var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
                if (response.success && response.success === true) {
                    var filteredProducts = response.products.map(function(el) {
                        if (el.product.published !== false && el.product.purchasable !== false) {

                            var tempEl = {};
                            tempEl.id = el.product.id;
                            tempEl.prices = el.product.prices;
                            tempEl.prices.forEach(function(el2) {
                                el2.price = el2.originalPrice||el2.formattedLowestPrice;
                                delete el2.originalPrice;
                                delete el2.label;
                                delete el2.isLoyalty;
                                delete el2.opportunidadUnica;
                                delete el2.symbol;

                            });
                            return tempEl;

                        }
                    });
                  if(callback){
                       callback(filteredProducts);
                  }else{
                    console.log(filteredProducts);
                  }


                }

                if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
                     callback(null);

                }
        });

        fetchItemDetailRequest.open("GET", fetchItemDetailURL, true);
        fetchItemDetailRequest.send();
    }
}

window.fetchProductUpdatedInfo=fetchProductUpdatedInfo;

var ui = {
    isSLP: function () {
        if (digitalData.page.catalyst) {
            return true;
        }
        return false;
    },
    str: function str() {
        return 'T|x|x|x|x|x|x|x';

    },
    approvedTrackClick: function approvedTrackClick(menulink) {
        var isMenuLink = false;
        if (/(ThirdLevelItems|SecondLevelItems|ToggleThirdCategories|thirdLevelMenu)/.test(menulink.className) || menulink && menulink.parentElement && /secondLevelMenu__/.test(menulink.parentElement.className) || menulink.closest('[class*="thirdLevelMenu__mobile"]')) {
            isMenuLink = true;
        }
        if (!isMenuLink)
            return;
        var finalCondition = false;
        finalCondition = isMenuLink;
        return finalCondition;
    },
    firstLevelDescription: function () {
        var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;
        if (ui.isSLP()) {
            var menuItems = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="firstLevelMenu__"] li');
            menuItemsArr = [].slice.apply(menuItems);
            var a = menuItemsArr.find(function (element, i) {
                if (/active/.test(element.className)) {
                    return element;
                }
            });
            return windowW ? document.querySelector('[class*="firstLevelMenu__title--active"]').textContent.trim() : a.textContent.trim();
        } else {
            return windowW ? document.querySelector("#mobile-item-".concat(ui.firstLevelPosition())).textContent.trim() : document.querySelector("#item-".concat(ui.firstLevelPosition())).textContent.trim();
        }
    },
    firstLevelPosition: function () {
        var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;
        if (ui.isSLP()) {
            if (windowW) {
                var index = false;
                var menuItems = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="firstLevelMenu__title"]');
                menuItemsArr = [].slice.apply(menuItems);
                menuItemsArr.map(function (element, i) {
                    if (/--active/.test(element.className)) {
                        index = i;
                    }
                });
                return index;
            } else {
                var index = false;
                var menuItems = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="firstLevelMenu__"] li');
                menuItemsArr = [].slice.apply(menuItems);
                menuItemsArr.map(function (element, i) {
                    if (/active/.test(element.className)) {
                        index = i;
                    }
                });
                return index;
            }
        } else {
            var index = false;
            var section = window.screen.width < 1024 ? document.querySelectorAll("section[class*='menuSection'] section") : document.querySelectorAll("section[class*='menuSection'] > div > section");
            section = Array.from(section);
            section.map(function (element, i) {
                if (/display/.test(element.className)) {
                    index = i;
                }
            });

            return index;
        }
    },
    secondLevelDescription: function (theParent) {
        var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;

        if (ui.isSLP()) {
            if (windowW) {
                return theParent.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"]').querySelector('a').textContent.trim()
            } else {
                return theParent.querySelector('[class*="secondLevelMenu__title"]').textContent.trim();
            }

        } else {
            if (windowW) {
                return theParent.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_detailsElementsSmallDevice"]') ? theParent.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_detailsElementsSmallDevice"]').querySelector('a,p').textContent.trim() : theParent.closest('[class*=ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel]').previousSibling.querySelector('a,p').textContent.trim()
            } else {
                return theParent.querySelector('[class*="SecondLevelItems_submenuTitle"]').textContent.trim();

            }
        }
    },
    order: function order(el, type) {
        var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;
        var order = false;
        var menuLink = el;
        var columnOrder = function () {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                return windowW ? menuLink.closest("[class*=firstLevelMenu__content]").parentElement.parentElement.querySelectorAll('[class*="firstLevelMenu"]') : menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenuContainer"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="secondLevelMenu__dekstop"]');
            } else {
                return windowW ? menuLink.closest("[class*=SecondLevelItems_displaySubMenuMobile]").parentElement.querySelectorAll("section") : menuLink.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_displaySubMenuDesktop"]').querySelectorAll('ul');
            }
        };
        columnOrder = [].slice.apply(columnOrder());
        if (windowW && type === "column") {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                var newMenuLink = menuLink.closest("[class*=firstLevelMenu__content]");
                var newMenuLinkArr = [].slice.apply(newMenuLink.querySelectorAll('[class*="secondLevelMenu"]'));
                return newMenuLinkArr.indexOf(menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu"]'))
            } else {
                var subElementsMobile = menuLink.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_submenuElements"]');
                var subElementsArr = [].slice.apply(subElementsMobile.querySelectorAll('[class*="SecondLevelItems_detailsElementsSmallDevice"],[class*="ThirdLevelItems_desactiveMobileThirdLevel"],[class*="ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel"]'));
                var newMenuLink = menuLink.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_detailsElementsSmallDevice"],[class*="ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel"],[class*="ThirdLevelItems_desactiveMobileThirdLevel"]')

                return Math.ceil((subElementsArr.indexOf(newMenuLink) + 1) / 2) - 1;
            }

        }
        //desktop
        if (!windowW && type === "column") {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                return columnOrder.indexOf(menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu"]'));

            } else {
                return columnOrder.indexOf(menuLink.closest('ul'));

            }

        }
        //mobile
        if (windowW && type === "row") {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                if (menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__title"]')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var thirdLevelContainer = menuLink.closest('[class*="thirdLevelMenu__mobile"]');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(thirdLevelContainer.querySelectorAll('li'));
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('li');
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;

                }

            } else {
                if (menuLink.closest('[class*=SecondLevelItems_detailsElementsSmallDevice]')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var thirdLevelContainer = menuLink.closest('[class*=ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel]');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(thirdLevelContainer.querySelectorAll('li'));
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('li');
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;
                }

            }

        }

        if (!windowW && type === "row") {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                if (menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__title"]')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var thirdLevelContainer = menuLink.closest('[class*="thirdLevelMenu"]');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(thirdLevelContainer.querySelectorAll('li'));
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('li');
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;

                }

            } else {
                if (menuLink.closest('[class*=SecondLevelItems_submenuTitleCon]')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_listElements"]');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(menuLink.closest('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_leafNodes"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_listElements"]'));
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;
                }
                return;
            }

        }
        var filterColum = function () {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                if (windowW) {
                    var a = columnOrder.find(function (el) {
                        if (el.querySelector('[class*="secondLevelMenu__title--active"]')) {
                            return el.querySelector('[class*="secondLevelMenu__title--active"]');
                        }
                    });
                    return [].slice.apply(a.querySelectorAll('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"]'));
                } else {
                    return columnOrder;
                }
            } else {
                return columnOrder;
            }
        };
        filterColum().map(function (el, i) {
            var rgx = el.textContent;

            var title = function () {
                if (ui.isSLP()) {
                    return el.innerText.split("\n", 1)[0];
                } else {
                    return el.textContent.substr(0, secondLevelDescription.length);
                }
            };

            var theParent = function () {
                if (windowW) {
                    return linkTo;
                } else {
                    if (menuLink.className.indexOf("thirdLevelMenu--link") > -1 || menuLink.className.indexOf("ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLi") > -1) {
                        return ui.isSLP() ? menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement : menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement
                    } else {
                        return menuLink.parentElement.parentElement;
                    }
                }
            };
            var secondLevelDescription = ui.secondLevelDescription(theParent());

            if (title() === secondLevelDescription) {

                if (rgx.indexOf(menuLink.textContent.trim()) > -1) {
                    var indexColumn = i;
                    var thisSlpTitle = ui.isSLP() ? /__title/.test(menuLink.className) : /_submenuTitle/.test(menuLink.className);
                    if (thisSlpTitle) {
                        if (menuLink.textContent === el.querySelector('[class*="_submenuTitle"]').textContent) {
                            switch (type) {
                                case "column":
                                    order = indexColumn;
                                    break;
                                case "row":
                                    order = /\<\/a>/.test(menuLink.outerHTML) ? indexColumn = 0 : indexColumn + 1;
                                    break;
                                default:
                                    console.log("not column or row");
                                    break;
                            }
                        }
                    } else {
                        var isSLPListElement = ui.isSLP() ? el.querySelectorAll('li') : el.querySelectorAll("[class*=ThirdLevelItems_listElements]");
                        // var thirdLink = windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=thirdLevelMenu') : isSLPListElement;
                        var thirdLink = function () {
                            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                                return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"] [class*="secondLevelMenu__content"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=thirdLevelMenu') : isSLPListElement;
                            } else {
                                // return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_displaySubMenuMobile"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel] li') : isSLPListElement;
                                return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="activeMobileThirdLevel"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=ThirdLevelItems]') : isSLPListElement;
                            }
                        };
                        thirdLink = [].slice.apply(thirdLink());
                        thirdLink.map(function (el, i) {
                            if (el.textContent.trim() === menuLink.textContent.trim()) {
                                switch (type) {
                                    case "column":
                                        order = indexColumn;
                                        break;
                                    case "row":
                                        order = ui.isSLP() ? i - 1 : i + 1;
                                        break;
                                    default:
                                        console.log("not column or row");
                                        break;
                                }
                            }
                        });
                    }
                }
            }
        });
        return order;
    }
};

function execute() {
    var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;
    var topLevelMenu = document.querySelector('[class*="hamburgerBtn"]') ? document.querySelectorAll('[class*="hamburgerBtn"]') : document.querySelectorAll('.fb-masthead__new-hamburger-menu [class*="_firstCategories"],[class*="CategoryMenuButton-module_menu-toggle-button"]');
    var validateServer = digitalData.page.serverName;
    if (topLevelMenu.length === 0)
        return;
    document.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
        var menuLink = windowW ? event.target : event.target.closest('a');
        if (menuLink && ui.approvedTrackClick(menuLink)) {
            var firstLevelPosition = ui.firstLevelPosition() + 1;
            var firstLevelDescription = ui.firstLevelDescription();
            var linkTo = event.target || event.target.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('[class*="submenuTitleToggleActive"]');
            var theParent = function () {
                if (windowW) {
                    return linkTo;
                } else {
                    if (menuLink.className.indexOf("thirdLevelMenu--link") > -1 || menuLink.className.indexOf("ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLi") > -1) {
                        return ui.isSLP() ? menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement : menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement
                    } else {
                        return menuLink.parentElement.parentElement;
                    }
                }
            };
            var secondLevelDescription = ui.secondLevelDescription(theParent());
            var thirdLevelDescription = menuLink.textContent.trim() !== "" && menuLink.textContent.trim() !== "arrow" ? menuLink.textContent.trim() : secondLevelDescription;

            var columnOrder = ui.order(menuLink, 'column');
            var rowOrder = ui.order(menuLink, 'row') === -1 ? 0 : ui.order(menuLink, 'row');

            if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                localStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str());
                //sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

            }

            sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', firstLevelDescription + '|' + secondLevelDescription + '|' + thirdLevelDescription + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + columnOrder + '|' + rowOrder);

        }
        if (/img_banner/.test(event.target.className)) {
            var firstLevelPosition = ui.firstLevelPosition();
            var topCategory = event.target.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.closest('[class*="submenuStage"]').querySelector('[class*="FirstLevelItems_menuElementsHover"]').textContent;
            var ImgName = event.target.src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg/)[0].replace('?', '');
            if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                localStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str());
            }
            sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', topCategory + '|' + 'B1' + '|' + ImgName + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + '50' + '|' + '1');
        }
        if (event.target.closest('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_category-content-container"],[class*="CategoryMenuMobile-module_mobile-menu-container"]')) {
            if (window.screen.width < 1024) {
                //dosomething
                if (event.target.closest('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]') || event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]') && event.target.localName !== "svg" && !/CategoryMenuButton-module_hamburger/i.test(event.target.className)) {
                    var columnCollection = [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[data-testid="first-level-category"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]'));
                    var linksCollection = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]') ? [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="MenuBody-module_leaf-category-item"]')) : [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]').parentElement.parentElement.querySelectorAll('[class*="MenuBody-module_leaf-category-item"]'));
                    var firstLevelCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-1"]'));

                    var firstLevelPosition = firstLevelCollection.indexOf(document.querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-1][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]')) + 1;
                    var firstLevelDescription = document.querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-1][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]').innerText;
                    var columnOrder = columnCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="first-level-category"]').querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-2][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]'));
                    if (columnCollection[columnOrder] === undefined) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var secondLevelDescription = columnCollection[columnOrder].innerText;
                    var thirdLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]') ? event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]').innerText : columnCollection[columnOrder].innerText;
                    var rowOrder = !event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]') ? 0 : linksCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]')) + 1;
                    if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                        localStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str());
                        //sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

                    }
                    sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', firstLevelDescription + '|' + secondLevelDescription + '|' + thirdLevelDescription + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + columnOrder + '|' + rowOrder);

                }
            } else {
                if (event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') || ('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]')) {
                    var columnCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[class*="SubCategories-module_tab-container"] ul'));
                    var linksCollection = [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('ul').querySelectorAll('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]'));
                    var firstLevelCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[data-testid="desktop-menu-category-button"]'))

                    var firstLevelPosition = firstLevelCollection.indexOf(document.querySelector('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_active"]')) + 1;
                    var firstLevelDescription = document.querySelector('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_active"] span').innerText;
                    var columnOrder = columnCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('ul'));
                    var secondLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText : event.target.closest('ul').querySelector('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText;
                    var thirdLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText : event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]').innerText;
                    var rowOrder = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? 0 : linksCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]')) + 1;
                    if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                        localStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str());
                        //sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

                    }
                    sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', firstLevelDescription + '|' + secondLevelDescription + '|' + thirdLevelDescription + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + columnOrder + '|' + rowOrder);

                }

            }
        }
    });
}

execute();

<script>_satellite["_runScript22"](function(event, target, Promise) {
function isDeviceMobile() {
    var isMobile = false;
    if (/Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|BB|PlayBook|IEMobile|Windows Phone|Kindle|Silk|Opera Mini/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
        isMobile = true;
    }
    return isMobile;
}

function changeMobile() {
	var chanelText = document.querySelectorAll('b.pod-title');
	var buttonChanel = document.querySelectorAll('.pod-button-add-to-cart');
	var isButton = false;
	if(buttonChanel) {
	isButton = true;
	}
	if (chanelText) {
	var fragrances =  document.querySelectorAll('span.high');
	if (fragrances) {
		for (var i = 0; i < chanelText.length; i ++) {
		if (chanelText[i].innerText === "CHANEL") {
			var rating = fragrances[i].parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('.pod-rating.pod-rating-2_GRID');
			if (rating) {
			rating.style.display = "none";
			}
			fragrances[i].classList.remove('high');
			if (isButton) {
			buttonChanel[i].parentElement.style.background = "black";
			}
		}
		}
	}
	} 
}

function changeDesktop() {
	var chanelText = document.querySelectorAll('b.pod-title');
	var buttonChanel = document.querySelectorAll('.pod-button-add-to-cart');
	var isButton = false;
	if(buttonChanel) {
	isButton = true;
	}
	if (chanelText) {
	var fragrances =  document.querySelectorAll('span.high');
	if (fragrances) {
		for (var i = 0; i < chanelText.length; i ++) {
		if (chanelText[i].innerText === "CHANEL") {
			var rating = fragrances[i].parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('.pod-rating.pod-rating-4_GRID');
			if (rating) {
			rating.style.display = "none";
			}
			fragrances[i].classList.remove('high');
			if (isButton) {
			buttonChanel[i].parentElement.style.background = "black";
			}
		}
		}
	}
	} 
}

if(!isDeviceMobile()) {
    changeDesktop();
} else {
    changeMobile();
}

function addIsPLP() {
    //add isPLP desktop and mobile -
    var linksMenu = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLiBold"]');
    linksMenu.forEach(function (el, index) {
        el.href = el.href + '?isPLP=1';
    });
}
function addIsPLPexplorer() {
    var a = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLiBold"]');
    for (i = 0; i < a.length; i++) {
        a[i].href = a[i].href + '?isPLP=1';
    }

}
function isIE() {
    ua = navigator.userAgent;
    /* MSIE used to detect old browsers and Trident used to newer ones*/
    var is_ie = ua.indexOf("MSIE ") > -1 || ua.indexOf("Trident/") > -1;
    return is_ie;
}
function executeIsPLP() {
    /* Create an alert to show if the browser is IE or not */
    if (isIE()) {
        setTimeout(addIsPLPexplorer, 1000);
    } else {
        addIsPLP();
    }
}
executeIsPLP();

    if (containerMobile) {
        var optionsFilter = containerMobile.querySelectorAll('li');

            for(var i = 0; i < optionsFilter.length; i++) {
                if (optionsFilter[i].innerText === 'MÁS COMENTADOS') {
                    optionsFilter[i].style.display = "none";
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

    setInterval(hideFilterMobile, 1000);

    hideFilterDesktop();

//funcion de mabaya
function isCategory() {
    return /\/category\//.test(document.URL) ? true : false;
}

function widgetType(bool) {
    if (bool) {
        return "widgets=gallery_page_g1";
    } else {
        return "widgets=search_page_w1";
    }

}

function getSection(bool) {
    if (bool) {

        var match = document.URL.match(/cat\d+\/(.*)\?|cat\d+\/(.*)$/);
        var section = match[2] ? match[2] : match[1];
        return section.toLowerCase();
    } else {
         var queryString = window.location.search;
        var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(queryString);
        var redirectValue=urlParams.get('sred');
        if(redirectValue){
            return redirectValue.toLowerCase();
        }
        if(_satellite.getVar('search_SearchTerm')){
          return _satellite.getVar('search_SearchTerm').replace('BCR_', '').toLowerCase();
        }
        
        return document.URL.split('/')[5];
    }

}
function deleteExtraClones() {
    document.querySelectorAll('.mabayaClone').forEach(function(el) {
        el.remove();
    });
}

function showOrhideDuplicates(arr) {
    if (arr) {
        arr.forEach(function(el) {
            var duplicatePod = document.querySelector('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"], .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"], .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone) .pod-head a[href*="' + el.product.productId + '"]');
            if (duplicatePod && duplicatePod.closest('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)')) {
                duplicatePod.closest('.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)').classList.add('hide');
            }
        });
    } else {
        if (document.querySelector('.hide.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)')) {
            document.querySelector('.hide.search-results-list:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-4-grid:not(.mabayaClone), .hide.search-results-2-grid:not(.mabayaClone)').classList.remove('hide');

        }
    }

}

function isFirstPage() {
    return true;
}
function isGoodOrderBy() {
    if (/marca|precio/i.test(_satellite.getVar('PLPOrderby'))) {
        return false
    }
    return true;
}
function getTag() {

    var params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.href);
    var arr = [];
    var _iteratorNormalCompletion = true;
    var _didIteratorError = false;
    var _iteratorError = undefined;

    try {
        for (var _iterator = params.entries()[Symbol.iterator](), _step; !(_iteratorNormalCompletion = (_step = _iterator.next()).done); _iteratorNormalCompletion = true) {
            pair = _step.value;
            var a = pair[0] + ": " + decodeURIComponent(pair[1]);
            var b = a.replace("::", " | ");
            arr.push(b);
        }
    } catch (err) {
        _didIteratorError = true;
        _iteratorError = err;
    } finally {
        try {
            if (!_iteratorNormalCompletion && _iterator.return != null) {
                _iterator.return();
            }
        } finally {
            if (_didIteratorError) {
                throw _iteratorError;
            }
        }
    }

    var newArr = arr.filter(function(el, index) {
        var temp;
        if (index === 0 && /\?/.test(el)) {
            temp = el.match(/\?(.*)/)[1];
        }
        if (index > 0) {

            temp = el;
        }
        if (/f\./.test(temp) && !/price|brand/.test(temp)) {

            return temp;
        }
    });
    var arr2 = newArr.map(function(a) {
        //return a.match(/\:(.*)/)[1].replace(/^\s/gi, '').replace(/\s\|\s|\:\:/gi, '|').toLowerCase();
        return a.match(/\:(.*)/)[1].replace(/\s/gi, '').replace(/\:\:/gi, '|').toLowerCase();
    }).join('|');

    if (arr2 === "") {
        return '';
    } else {
        return 'tag:' + arr2 + ',';
    }
}

function mabayaAdRequest(callback, callback2) {
    var IsCategory = isCategory();
    var storeHash = "storeHash=570436b118e98697c04269e8ee598adfd5e1f5a7f2fe3dab21da19f1c04fbd2b";
    var pageTypeParam = IsCategory ? "pageType=category" : "pageType=search";
    var mabayaRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
    var signal = "signal=" + encodeURIComponent(getSection(IsCategory)).toLowerCase();
    var ufObject = {
        brands: '',
        minPrice: '',
        maxPrice: '',
        cat: IsCategory ? "cid:" + document.URL.match(/(cat\d+)\//)[1] + "," : ""
    };

    var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
    if (urlParams.get('f.product.brandName') !== null) {

        urlParams.get('f.product.brandName').split('::').forEach(function(el) {
            ufObject.brands = ufObject.brands + 'brand:' + el.toLowerCase() + ',';
        });
    }
    var customPrice = urlParams.get('r.derived.price.search');
    if (urlParams.get('r.derived.price.search') !== null) {
        ufObject.minPrice = 'minPrice:' + customPrice.split('::')[1] + ',';
        ufObject.maxPrice = 'maxPrice:' + customPrice.split('::')[0] + ',';
    }

    var rangePrice = urlParams.get('f.range.derived.price.search');
    if (rangePrice !== null) {
        ufObject.minPrice = 'minPrice:' + rangePrice.split(' - ')[0].replace(/\$|\./g, '') + ',';
        ufObject.maxPrice = 'maxPrice:' + rangePrice.split(' - ')[1].replace(/\$|\./g, '') + ',';

    }
    var ufParam = "uf=" + encodeURIComponent(ufObject.cat + ufObject.brands + ufObject.minPrice + ufObject.maxPrice + getTag());
var ufPlatform= screen.width>1024?"desktop":"mobile";
    var paramString = widgetType(IsCategory) + "&" + storeHash + "&" + pageTypeParam + "&platform="+ufPlatform + "&" + signal + "&" + ufParam + "&url=" + encodeURIComponent(document.URL).toLowerCase();
    var mabayaURL = "https://us.widget.mb-srv.com/v2/server2server/ad.json?" + paramString;
    deleteExtraClones();
    showOrhideDuplicates();
    mabayaRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {
        var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
        if (isFirstPage() && isGoodOrderBy() && response.code && response.code === "OK" && response.payload.ads.length > 0) {
            if (callback) {

                //showOrhideDuplicates(response.payload.ads);
                callback(response.payload.ads, callback2);
            } else {
                console.log(response);
            }

        } else {
            console.log("no mabaya pods");
        }
        if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
            console.log("Error retrieving mabaya products")

        }
    });

    mabayaRequest.open("GET", mabayaURL, true);
    mabayaRequest.send();
}

function fixArr(arr) {
    if (typeof (arr) === "object" && arr[0] && arr[0].skuId) {
        return arr;
    }

    if (typeof (arr) === undefined) {
        return null;
    }
    var temporalArr = [];
    if (Array.isArray(arr)) {
        temporalArr = arr;
    }
    if (typeof (arr) === "string") {
        temporalArr = arr.split(",");
    }

    var fixedArray = []
    temporalArr.forEach(function(el) {
        fixedArray.push({
            "skuId": el
        });
    });
    return fixedArray;

}
function fetchProductUpdatedInfo(skuArr, callback) {
    //XMLHttpRequest
    window.mabayaIDs = {}
    skuArr.forEach(function(el) {
        window.mabayaIDs[el.sku] = el.mabaya_ad_info;
    });
    if (skuArr) {
        var newArr = skuArr.map(function(e) {
            return e.sku
        });

        var fetchItemDetailRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
        var fetchItemDetailURL = "/s/browse/v1/fetchItemDetails/co?" + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify({
            "products": fixArr(newArr)
        }));

        fetchItemDetailRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {

            var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
            if (response.success && response.success === true) {
                if (callback) {
                    showOrhideDuplicates(response.products);

                    callback(response.products);
                } else {
                    console.log(response.products, skuArr);
                }
            }

            if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
                callback(null);

            }
        });

        fetchItemDetailRequest.open("GET", fetchItemDetailURL, true);
        fetchItemDetailRequest.send();
    }
}
function patrocinadoLabel() {
    var pLabel = document.createElement('div');
    pLabel.classList.add('pod-sponsored-prod')
    pLabel.innerText = "Patrocinado";
    return pLabel;
}

function clonePodsWithInfo(res, objArr) {
    res.forEach(function(e, index) {
        
        if (document.querySelectorAll('.mabayaClone').length >= 6 || e.product.published != true) {
            return;
        }

        var allPods = document.querySelectorAll('.search-results-list:not(.mabaya), .search-results-4-grid:not(.mabaya), .search-results-2-grid:not(.mabaya)');

        if (index >= 2) {
            var repeatFlag = false;
            for (var i = 0; i > 12; i++) {
                if (allPods[i] !== undefined && allPods[i].querySelector('[data-key]').dataset.key == e.product.id) {
                    repeatFlag = true;

                }
            }
            if (repeatFlag) {
                return
            }

        }

        var newPod = allPods[0].cloneNode(true);
        newPod.classList.add("mabayaClone");
        newPod.classList.remove("hide");
        var mbid = window.mabayaIDs && window.mabayaIDs[e.product.id] ? window.mabayaIDs[e.product.id] : "";
        newPod.dataset.mbid = mbid;
        var mbidParam = mbid ? "&mbid=" + mbid : "";
        newPod.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(function(l) {
            l.href = e.product.url + "?MID=SP" + mbidParam;
        })

        newPod.querySelector('img').src = "https://falabella.scene7.com/is/image/FalabellaCO/" + e.product.id + "?wid=340&hei=340&qlt=70";
        newPod.querySelector('img').srcset = "https://falabella.scene7.com/is/image/FalabellaCO/" + e.product.id + "?wid=340&hei=340&qlt=70";
        if (e.product.badges && newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper')) {
            newPod.querySelectorAll('[class*=pod-badges-item]').forEach(function(badge) {
                badge.remove();
            });
            e.product.badges.forEach(function(badge) {
                var newBadge = document.querySelector('[class*=pod-badges-item]').cloneNode(true);

                newBadge.style.backgroundColor = badge.styles.backgroundColor;
                newBadge.style.textColor = badge.styles.textColor;
                newBadge.innerHTML = badge.label;
                newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper .pod-badges').appendChild(newBadge);
            });
        } else if (!e.product.badges && newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-badges-LIST,.badges-wrapper .pod-badges').remove();
        }

        var bottomSpecifications = newPod.querySelector('.section__pod-bottom-description');

        if (bottomSpecifications) {
            bottomSpecifications.innerHTML = "";
            e.product.topSpecifications.forEach(function(el3) {

                var newSpecification = document.querySelector('.section__pod-bottom-description>li').cloneNode(false);
                newSpecification.innerText = el3;

                bottomSpecifications.appendChild(newSpecification);
            })

        }

        newPod.querySelectorAll('.ratings--container i').forEach(function(star, index) {

            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_full_filled');
            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_no_filled');
            star.classList.remove('csicon-star_half_filled');
            if (e.product.rating < 0 + 1) {
                star.classList.add("csicon-star_no_filled")
            } else {
                star.classList.add("csicon-star_full_filled");
            }
        });
        if (newPod.querySelector('.reviewCount')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.reviewCount').remove();
        }

        if (newPod.querySelector('.fa--color-swatch')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.fa--color-swatch').remove();
        }

        if (newPod.querySelector('.tab')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.tab').remove();
        }
        //csicon-star_full_filled
        //csicon-star_no_filled
        if (newPod.querySelector('.pod-subTitle')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-subTitle').innerText = e.product.displayName;
        }
        if (e.product.brand && newPod.querySelector('.pod-title')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-title').innerText = e.product.brand;
        }else{
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-title').remove();
        }

        if(newPod.querySelector('.pod-sellerText')){
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-sellerText').innerText="Por Falabella";
        }

            makeNewPrices(newPod, e.product.prices);
      
      
        if (newPod.querySelector('.pod-meta') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.pod-meta').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), newPod.querySelector('[class*="action-button-place-holder"]'));
        } else if (newPod.querySelector('.section-body--right') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {

            newPod.querySelector('.section-body--right').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), null);

        } else if (newPod.querySelector('.section-head') && !newPod.querySelector('.pod-sponsored-prod')) {
            newPod.querySelector('.section-head').insertBefore(patrocinadoLabel(), null);
        }

        var childRefNode;
        if (index < 2) {
            childRefNode = allPods[0];
        } else if (index < 4) {
            childRefNode = allPods[13];
        } else {
            childRefNode = null;
        }

        document.querySelector('.search-results--products').insertBefore(newPod, childRefNode);

    });
    if (window.mabayaWidget) {
        window.mabayaWidget.track();
    }
}
//extension resource overrides

function makeNewPrices(node, price) {

    node.querySelectorAll('.fa--prices .price-0,.fa--prices .price-1,.fa--prices .price-2').forEach(function(el) {
        el.remove();
    });
    if (price[0]) {
        var newPrice = document.querySelector('.fa--prices .price-0').cloneNode(true);
        newPrice.querySelector('span').innerText = price[0].symbol + " " + price[0].originalPrice + " " + price[0].label;

        node.querySelector('.fa--prices').appendChild(newPrice);

    }
    if (price[1]) {
        var newPriceTwo = document.querySelector('.fa--prices .price-1').cloneNode(true)
        newPriceTwo.querySelector('span').innerText = price[1].symbol + " " + price[1].originalPrice + " " + price[1].label;
        node.querySelector('.fa--prices').appendChild(newPriceTwo);

    }

}
